Agentic-Base Library — Full Specification
 Agentic-Base  is the foundational agent infrastructure library for the entire SLM/LLM Drone/Swarm Orchestration project. It acts as the single source of truth for every agent SDK, class, harness, configuration, and inter-agent contract used across all DPR modules (VPS, DOOAF, IDF).[marktechpost]
---
Position in the Architecture
 Agentic-Base  sits at Layer 0 — below all mission logic, drone controllers, fleet managers, and vision systems. Every module that spawns, invokes, or communicates with an agent imports from Agentic-Base. It is never a runtime service itself — it is a compiled library dependency.[fratepietro]

