Library Structure

agentic_base/
│
├── core/
│   ├── agent_base.py           # Abstract base class: BaseAgent
│   ├── sub_agent.py            # SubAgent class, parent-child contracts
│   ├── agent_group.py          # AgentGroup (collective behavior, quorum)
